        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 604dfbdb-1cdd-4d96-ba13-7a7dacbc973c).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rAfter dealing with the primary target, Alexa Carlisle, it was revealed that her niece (and daughter-in-lie), Emma, was the cause of Zachary Carlisle&apos;s murder.\r\rWith some additional intel, we have found that she had some help from the security guard, Ben Moore. She has also managed to bribe Aron Ford Jr., the lawyer Alexa Carlisle had hired. \r\rDeal with Emma and her accomplices while leaving something behind that would tie Fernsby to the murders.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
        "GameVersion": "8.7.0.0",
